960
01:20:59,832 --> 01:21:02,068
Take your courage
and leave me be

961
01:21:18,865 --> 01:21:20,872
Oh, don't go!

962
01:21:20,977 --> 01:21:23,791
- I'm just gonna
get you some water
- Oh, not yet, please

963
01:21:23,888 --> 01:21:27,367
I don't wanna go to sleep yet
I just want to talk to you

964
01:21:28,462 --> 01:21:30,763
Take me away, Mitch

965
01:21:30,861 --> 01:21:32,683
